ning the magnetically-dominated\nstructure close to the binary. Our result may provide an explanation for the\ncircumbinary disks detected in recent SMA and ALMA observations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Aug 2013 18:20:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-08-06"}
