c quantum memories\nallows a feasible experimental realization within existing technologies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Aug 2013 19:07:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 10 Nov 2013 10:23:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 May 2014 18:44:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-05-29"}
